data.description: Lovely 2 Story home is ready for new owners! Welcome to this 4 Bedrooms, 3 Baths home with 3 car garages and NO HOA fee! Enter to your main floor with Office Room and Formal Dining.   Living room with Fireplace and open concept layout to the kitchen and one bathroom. Kitchen remodeled with NEW Cabinets, Appliances, Backsplash, Flooring and Counter Seating. The Washer and Dryer is included. Upstairs to 4 Bedrooms with each own closets.   Master bedroom got its own Walk-in Closet and Bathroom space with new Cabinets, Lighting and Toilet. Additional Full Bath and Laundry complete this level. You will enjoy your FINISHED Basement with large rec room.   Your 0.6 acre beautiful corner lot is landscaped with Large Deck. BRAND NEW ROOF just installed! Close location to shopping/dining about 3 minutes and took 12 minutes from South Lake Mall. The house located in a nice lot and quiet neighborhood. Don't hesitate to make your appointment today!
